




=====konga====
$ git clone https://github.com/pantsel/konga.git
$ cd konga
$ cnpm i

cp .env_example .env

.env 内容
PORT=8090
NODE_ENV=production
DB_ADAPTER=postgres
DB_HOST =127.0.0.1
DB_PORT =5432
DB_USER =konga
DB_DATABASE =konga
KONGA_LOG_LEVEL=warn

创建迁移
node ./bin/konga.js  prepare --adapter postgres --uri postgresql://konga:123456@localhost:5432/konga
启动
 npm start
npm run production
